                    <provenance>
                      The name of a former owner, <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS12722WaldaMikael">
                    Walda Mikāʾel</persName>, is inserted over erasure on f. 5 and f. 25.
                      The manuscript was bought in Ethiopia by the Russian diplomat
                       <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7674Orlov">Alexander Orlov</persName>.</provenance>
                      <acquisition>The manuscript was acquired by the Asiatic
                        Museum on <date>10 September 1903</date>.
                    </acquisition>
               </history>

